{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9a16409e46","title":"为瑞金红军烈士纪念塔写的碑文","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7d468a829a","index":0,"year":1934,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"9a16409e46"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-1","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"62eae52640","type":"paragraph","text":"为瑞金红军烈士纪念塔写的碑文！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"4e993d7955","type":"paragraph","text":"（1934年1月15日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"125903e755","type":"paragraph","text":"在反帝国主义与土地革命的伟大战斗中，许多同志光荣地栖性了！这些同志晒性，表现了无产阶级不可战胜的英勇，莫定了中华苏维埃共和国的基础，全中国工农劳苦群众，正在踏着这些同志的血迹前进，推翻帝国主义国民党的统治。争取苏维埃在全国的胜利。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"1087d3a3e6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"9a2ad41cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三四年一月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"e6e853b551","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1933年8月1日，为了纪念英勇辆牡的红军烈士，我党历史上第一座红军烈士纪念塔在红色国都瑞金的叶坪村动工。这是中华苏维埃共和国临时中央政府为迎接第二次全国苏维埃代表大会的召开而建立的。1934年1月","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"},{"id":"6bfde5e2de","type":"paragraph","text":"县室园医店瑞金红军烈士纪念塔。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46"}],"page":{"id":"6c3965f5a6","publicationId":"maoquanji7-1","articleId":"9a16409e46","start":163,"end":164}}}},"__N_SSG":true}